{
  "stem": "26983.12",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were losing strength and, in the periods in between, I would like to tell you a few--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Examples which I remember-- how the conditions were between us children, maybe from this group, we were about eight or 10, trying to stick together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once, one of us took something or stole from a woman, from this group of people who arrived from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in our eyes, that wasn't correct.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our punishment was that we didn't spoke with him--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't speak with him for one or two days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We put him in [NON-ENGLISH], in a ban.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was so unbearable for him, that he went to a kapo and sold himself to a homosexual couple.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everyone knew about it, that he, for this service, gives them a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He brought us the loaf of bread as if a kind of reconciliation with us, asking for forgiveness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember if we took it or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We accept him back, but if we also took the bread or let him eat  it alone, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right-- against our unwritten law.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were other things in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The conditions were very, very, bad, as I told you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the soup was distributed for the children in garbage container.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these garbage containers were loaded on, again, a kind of roll wagon, on wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, of the terrain, some of the drops of soup were spilled out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember a elderly-- in our eyes, elderly, at that time it's man of 30 or 40-- went with his kind of--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--pot he had, and tried-- from underneath the wagon, these dirty drops of soup, which runs through the thing-- to collect it, a few drops.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "SS man saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
